Her husband also opted for a blue suit to attend the event at the Palace today.

The Queen has been keeping busy, attending two events in two days already this week.

Yesterday, she showcased her elegant style once again in a floral Hugo Boss dress as she attended the opening of El Greco y La Pintura Moderna exhibition at El Prado museum in Madrid, Spain.

The 41-year-old teamed the pastel dress with nude courts, a notable favourite of the Duchess of Cambridge, with whom she's been compared on numerous occasions, as well as a matching waist belt and clutch bag.

